description: A small burbling brook runs parallel to the path here, set into the leeward side of the ridge.  A view of three-quarters of the island can be seen from here.  Colorful rocks protrude from the rich black soil, contrasting the iron and wood gates of residences.

title: [Boreas Ridge, Euros Plaza]
